messages.content: Anytime if you're starting with this, please let us know. We can definitely Collab and discuss
Got it. But yeah, would not fit us. Thanks again, for reaching out.
If you would like to know more and then if you're interested we can go further with the discussion.
We are not currently listing Bangalore/Karnataka.
Are you based out of Bangalore?
But I would like to know more
I am afraid we don't market projects/farm plots.

Hi..1acre.in
I hope this message finds you well, I am reaching out to discuss a potential collaboration opportunity with you.we've been following your work on Instagram and are impressed with your influence in real estate.
We have launched a new project called
Ardini Farms
Ecowood Habitat  and believe that your platform would be an excellent fit for promoting it to your engaged audience.
We would love to discuss the possibility of working together to create engaging content that showcases our project in a way that resonates with your followers.
If you are interested, I'd be happy to provide more details and discuss potential terms of collaboration further.
Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best regards,
Divya Thakkar
General Manager
Ardini Farms Ecowood Habitat
